{"tid":2389579,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"法文導讀 - J'irai au bout","createTime":"2021-02-01T04:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T13:22:00.000Z","uid":246823,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c40528ae35d1e10fd277665b25daa57458122e0b","tid":2389579,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"法文導讀 - J'irai au bout<br />\n<br />\n節錄自 LeFigaro<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lefigaro.fr/actualite-france/je-rouvrirai-le-1er-fevrier-l-appel-a-la-desobeissance-de-restaurateur-reste-isole-20210119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lefigaro.fr%2Factualite-france%2Fje-rouvrirai-le-1er-fevrier-l-appel-a-la-desobeissance-de-restaurateur-reste-isole-20210119&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G6P8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=f76c2409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lefigaro.fr/actualite-france/je-rouvrirai-le-1er-fevrier-l-appel-a-la-desobeissance-de-restaurateur-reste-isole-20210119</a><br />\n<br />\nPar Thomas Engrand<br />\nPubli&eacute; le 19/01/2021 &agrave; 18:17, mis &agrave; jour hier &agrave; 17:37<br />\n<br />\n🔈 <a href=\"https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/1.wav\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fncomplex.github.io%2Fmaterials%2Faudio%2Flefigaro-1%2F1.wav&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G6P8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=e628ad93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/1.wav</a><br />\n&laquo;J'irai <span class=\"orange\">au bout</span>&raquo; : ces restaurateurs <span class=\"orange\">en col&egrave;re</span><br />\nqui rouvriront leur &eacute;tablissement ce lundi<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><br />\n註:<br />\nJ'irai au bout: 我會去到盡<br />\nrestaurateur: 店主 (餐廳)<br />\nen col&egrave;re: 在怒<br />\n<br />\n解:<br />\n一班憤怒既店主, 由於不滿政府對佢地既防疫限制, 表明會去到盡 (無論如何都要開鋪做生意!!)<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n🔈 <a href=\"https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/2.wav\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fncomplex.github.io%2Fmaterials%2Faudio%2Flefigaro-1%2F2.wav&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G6P8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=65417d50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/2.wav</a><br />\nLanc&eacute;e par un restaurateur du Doubs, l'id&eacute;e d'ouvrir<br />\nmalgr&eacute; l'interdiction administrative <span class=\"orange\">a fait son chemin</span>.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><br />\n註:<br />\nfaire son chemin: 作其道 (決定進行)<br />\n<br />\n解:<br />\n唔理禁制, 決定去做<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n🔈 <a href=\"https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/3.wav\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fncomplex.github.io%2Fmaterials%2Faudio%2Flefigaro-1%2F3.wav&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G6P8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=1b99cd11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/3.wav</a><br />\nLa situation est de moins en moins <span class=\"orange\">tenable</span>, selon certains restaurateurs.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><br />\n註:<br />\ntenable: 從 &quot;se tenir&quot; (立), 從 se tenir + able (可站立)<br />\n<br />\n解:<br />\n某d店主表示情況已經忍無可忍<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n🔈 <a href=\"https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/4.wav\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fncomplex.github.io%2Fmaterials%2Faudio%2Flefigaro-1%2F4.wav&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G6P8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=b8e3da97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/4.wav</a><br />\nLe <span class=\"orange\">report</span> &agrave; une date inconnue de l'ouverture des restaurants<br />\na &eacute;t&eacute; tr&egrave;s <span class=\"orange\">mal v&eacute;cu</span> par leurs g&eacute;rants. Emp&ecirc;ch&eacute;s de travailler<br />\ndepuis des mois et financi&egrave;rement <span class=\"orange\">exsangues</span>,<br />\ncertains refusent de <span class=\"orange\">rester les bras crois&eacute;s</span>.<br />\nC'est le cas de St&eacute;phane Turillon, restaurateur &agrave; Cusance, dans le Doubs.<br />\nIl a d&eacute;cid&eacute; d'appeler ses pairs, partout en France,<br />\n&agrave; ouvrir ce 1er f&eacute;vrier pour le service de midi.<br />\nSon message a vite <span class=\"orange\">rencontr&eacute; un &eacute;cho</span> dans les m&eacute;dias<br />\net aupr&egrave;s de la population fran&ccedil;aise. Cependant la profession reste tr&egrave;s divis&eacute;e.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><br />\n註:<br />\nLe report: 推遲<br />\nune date inconnue: 無期<br />\nmal v&eacute;cu: 難以接受<br />\nexsangue: 失血<br />\nrester les bras crois&eacute;s: 繑埋雙手<br />\nrencontrer un &eacute;cho: 有回音<br />\n<br />\n解:<br />\n店主難以接受開業無期, 於是發起呼籲同行係2月1日集體開業, 獲得響應<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n🔈 <a href=\"https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/5.wav\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fncomplex.github.io%2Fmaterials%2Faudio%2Flefigaro-1%2F5.wav&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G6P8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=c63b6ad6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/5.wav</a><br />\nD&egrave;s le d&eacute;part, les restaurateurs affichant leur volont&eacute; de rouvrir<br />\nmalgr&eacute; l'interdiction n'ont pas r&eacute;ussi &agrave; parler d'une seule voix.<br />\nCertains, comme St&eacute;phane Turillon, appellent &agrave; une action &laquo;<span class=\"orange\">coup de poing</span>&raquo; :<br />\nouvrir les &eacute;tablissements ce 1er f&eacute;vrier uniquement, pour un service du midi.<br />\nLe tout <span class=\"orange\">dans le respect</span> des normes sanitaires et <span class=\"orange\">assez t&ocirc;t</span><br />\npour permettre &agrave; chacun de rentrer chez soi avant le couvre-feu.<br />\nSon but est de &laquo;prouver que les restaurants<br />\nne <span class=\"orange\">favorisent</span> pas la transmission du virus.&raquo;<br />\nD'autres aimeraient maintenir la r&eacute;ouverture les jours suivants.<br />\nEnfin quelques-uns ont d&eacute;cid&eacute; de se lancer seuls.<br />\nC'est le cas de Christophe Wilson &agrave; Nice, dont la r&eacute;ouverture<br />\nle 27 janvier pour une centaine de personnes a &eacute;t&eacute; particuli&egrave;rement <span class=\"orange\">m&eacute;diatis&eacute;e</span>.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><br />\n註:<br />\ncoup de poing: 拳擊<br />\ndans le respect de: 遵守<br />\nassez t&ocirc;t: 夠早<br />\nfavoriser: 有利於<br />\nm&eacute;diatis&eacute;: 見報<br />\n<br />\n解:<br />\n是次行動係為左表明餐廳唔會有利傳播病毒, 但有d人認為應該繼續等下, 有d就另外揀日子去服務特定某d人<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n🔈 <a href=\"https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/6.wav\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fncomplex.github.io%2Fmaterials%2Faudio%2Flefigaro-1%2F6.wav&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G6P8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=4552ba15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ncomplex.github.io/materials/audio/lefigaro-1/6.wav</a><br />\nUne chose les rassemble : tous veulent crier leur <span class=\"orange\">ras-le-bol</span>.<br />\nLe <span class=\"orange\">dispositif</span> d'aides mis en place par le gouvernement ne leur semble pas adapt&eacute;.<br />\n&laquo;Moi j'ai 15.000 euros de charges mensuelles, m&ecirc;me avec l'aide<br />\nje suis en d&eacute;ficit de 5000 euros&raquo;, explique un restaurateur mosellan<br />\nen r&eacute;f&eacute;rence au <span class=\"orange\">fonds</span> de solidarit&eacute; qui lui permet de toucher une aide mensuelle<br />\nmaximale de 10.000 euros. Le plus dur reste encore de ne pas conna&icirc;tre<br />\nla date officielle de r&eacute;ouverture. Ils attendent du gouvernement<br />\nl'annonce d'une date fixe, &laquo;m&ecirc;me si &ccedil;a doit &ecirc;tre le 1er juin&raquo;, <span class=\"orange\">glisse</span> l'un d'eux.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><br />\n註:<br />\nras-le-bol: 忍無可忍/受夠<br />\ndispositif: 計劃<br />\nfonds: 資金<br />\nglisser: 滑 (係人地講完一段說話後加以補充)<br />\n<br />\n解:<br />\n大家都忍無可忍, 政府既援助金根本唔夠, 比起援助金, 佢地要既係政府既畀出一個確實重開日期<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"90524592b35793b6cd83444f7ac3bac575580b77","tid":2389579,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"留名支持！"},{"pid":"40fa69eee6f8fc21e7ab99b6a6cf35e7b87762a4","tid":2389579,"uid":246823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"閱讀理解<br />\n1. Qu'est-ce qui a mis en col&egrave;re les restaurateurs ?<br />\n2. Qu'est-ce qu'on va faire dans l'action &laquo; coup de poing &raquo; ?<br />\n3. Combien peut un restaurant recevoir mensuellement comme aide financi&egrave;re ?<br />\n4. Les restaurateurs surtout que demandent-t-ils au gouvernement ?"},{"pid":"8d05d61270f201e42ca831fa19d0acaacfef55aa","tid":2389579,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64f89aa9938fe1842f560b6452f69e18900c21c","tid":2389579,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"LM溫習法文"},{"pid":"feed7c513ab02ac1d934570d2745532c173c70bb","tid":2389579,"uid":363953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:35:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2131fee203d4f9b34b3a77ebaa22f7a7aa2505a1","tid":2389579,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"France 24度揾？"},{"pid":"bc6070f6d56da78da1ee4ec5d8cb6bdc9cc26f27","tid":2389579,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2131fee203d4f9b34b3a77ebaa22f7a7aa2505a1","tid":2389579,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"France 24度揾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"lefigaro"},{"pid":"3c41f6aceebdc855d3a4057c4708e71a1cbcba3e","tid":2389579,"uid":169944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:47:02.00