2389579,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a237199e4443758a01e613b7b68f009072fcb42","tid":2389579,"uid":21249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:10:53.000Z","msg":"晚* <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:17:06.000Z","msg":"comment allez vous?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:17:35.000Z","msg":"即係咩意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:22:00.000Z","msg":"how are you咁解"}],"pinned":{"pid":"40fa69eee6f8fc21e7ab99b6a6cf35e7b87762a4","tid":2389579,"uid":246823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"閱讀理解<br />\n1. Qu'est-ce qui a mis en col&egrave;re les restaurateurs ?<br />\n2. Qu'est-ce qu'on va faire dans l'action &laquo; coup de poing &raquo; ?<br />\n3. Combien peut un restaurant recevoir mensuellement comme aide financi&egrave;re ?<br />\n4. Les restaurateurs surtout que demandent-t-ils au gouvernement ?"}}